WEBVTT

00:00:01.277 --> 00:00:05.135
(Phone) Stephanie Van Hasselt: Thank you
for calling Zappos, my name is Stephanie.

00:00:05.159 --> 00:00:06.366
How may I help you today?

00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:09.960
Adam Grant: One of my least favorite
things to do is call customer service.

00:00:09.984 --> 00:00:13.189
The cable company, my bank, tech support.

00:00:13.213 --> 00:00:14.363
It takes forever.

00:00:14.838 --> 00:00:16.991
You get put on hold over and over.

00:00:17.537 --> 00:00:20.244
How long was your last
customer service call?

00:00:20.664 --> 00:00:23.117
(Phone) SVH: But at least
you'd have your money,

00:00:23.141 --> 00:00:25.085
and it just depends...

00:00:25.109 --> 00:00:26.489
AdG: This call?

00:00:26.513 --> 00:00:31.202
It started around 9am
and it went for 11 hours.